title: ‘Atlanta’ Episode 19 and ‘Beverly Hills’ Episode 19
description:
Rachel begins this week’s 'Morally Corrupt' with a brief chat about Bravo news with Chelsea Stark-Jones (1:50), before Rachel and Chelsea move on to discuss the 'Real Housewives of Atlanta’ Season 14 reunion Part 2 (8:40). Rachel is then joined by Jodi Walker to break down Season 12, Episode 19 of ‘The Real Housewives of Beverly Hills’ (28:30).
Host: Rachel Lindsay
Guest: Chelsea Stark-Jones and Jodi Walker
Producers: Devon Manze
Theme Song: Devon Renaldo
